quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  4,27,"Nyankopֽ»n p־µs־µ ֶ†gye moadwen sakra, nanso wֽ»n a wֽ»ג€™di akֽ»nnֽ» akyire no hwehw־µ s־µ anka mob־µmane (afri kwan tenenee no so) akֽ» akyirikyiri paa"
  4,28,"Nyankopֽ»n p־µ s־µ ֶ†go (mmra) no mu ma mo, efiris־µ onipa mmֽ»e־µ anaa onipa suban mu no ֽ»y־µ abֽ»de־µ a ֽ»y־µ mmr־µ (onni ahoֽ»den)"
  4,29,"Mo a moagye adie, monhw־µ na moanfa nkontompo kwan so anni mont־µm sika, na mmom ־µny־µ s־µ adwadie a moate moho ase־µ; na monhw־µ na moankunkum moho. Nokor־µ s־µ Nyankopֽ»n hu mo mmֽ»bֽ»"
  4,30,"Na obi a ֽ»nam ֽ»tan ne asisie so b־µy־µ saa no, Y־µג€™de no b־µkֽ» Amanehunu gyem . Na ־µno de־µ ־µy־µ ade־µ a ־µy־µ mmer־µ koraa ma Nyankopֽ»n"
  4,31,"S־µ motwe mo ho firi bֽ»ne ak־µse־µ a yג€™abra mo no ho a, Yג€™־µb־µpepa mo bֽ»ne afri mo so, na Y־µג€™de mo akֽ»wura Animuonyam bea no mu"
  4,32,"Na monhw־µ na moany־µ aniberebere־µ wֽ» de־µ Nyankopֽ»n de ama ebinom aky־µn ebinom no ho. Mmarima wֽ» dwuma a wֽ»ג€™die ho akatua, ־µna mmaa nso wֽ» dwuma a wֽ»ג€™die ho akatua. Enti momisa adom mfiri Nyankopֽ»n (adom) no mu. Na Nyankopֽ»n ne biribiara ho Nimdefoֽ»"
  4,33,"Yג€™ahyehy־µ (obi a odi ade־µ) ama obiara fa agyapade־µ a awofoֽ» ne abusuafoֽ» bi (bewu) agya ho. Wֽ»n a mode monsa nifa ahy־µ (nkrataa) ase ne wֽ»n ahy־µ bֽ» wֽ» adedie ho no nso, monfa wֽ»n ky־µfa ma wֽ»n. Nokor־µ s־µ Nyankopֽ»n ne biribiara ho Dansefoֽ»"
